Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE HERO'S TUTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Army, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks very grim. Speed it up, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Gomechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip, Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like black blood\Nis coursing through my veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't stay focused,\NI think I'll go berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone suddenly became violent.\NWhat's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one possible reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Lord has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This urge to go berserk\Ncan only be the Dark Lord's evil will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wants to gather us with his dark power\Nto try to overthrow the world again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you must leave this island!\NOtherwise we might kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my good heart that let me raise you\Nafter you drifted here on this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I might harm you\Nwith my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run by myself!\NThat's not what a Hero would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said. You must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Master's got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark influence, begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mahokator!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude of me. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:06:01.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,I CAN TRAIN YOUR HERO!!\NA 15-YEAR VETERAN OF THE TRADE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,am a Hero trainer.\NBasically a tutor for Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero's tutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Agents of peace who uphold justice\Nand defeat evil! Heroes, Sages, Mages...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my job to train them\Ninto first-class warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is I, Avan De Zinuar III.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have I heard that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my student, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He is currently training to become a Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So why is such a tutor here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you've noticed\Nthat the Dark Lord has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters under his control are everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and people in places\Nlike Romos and Papnica are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! King Romos and Leona, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Papnica royal family\Nasked that I come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They want me to train the future Hero\Non Dermline Island to be a true Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, will you undergo my training?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to defeat the Dark Lord,\Nso it will be exceptionally hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! If Leona is in danger,\NI have to go help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, if we don't defeat the Dark Lord,\NGrampa and the others can't live in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please train me! I'll become a true Hero\Nand defeat the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gargoyles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A magic circle of light\Nhas sealed off the entire island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They appear to be\Nscouts for the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! By myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the purification spell, Mahokator,\Nso I am very, very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww. No fair, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push!\NI get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He trained that boy to be\Nsuch a powerful magic user!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems this man is the real deal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll roast you into fried chicken next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mahoton!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ka... Ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that Gargoyles can use\Nthe magic impairment spell, Mahoton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant of the Dark Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,get off of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You may use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a distinguished legendary sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take more than improvised swordplay\Nto defeat a soldier of the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really an amazing sword, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm. It's actually a cheap sword\NI bought at a used goods store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems this boy may be quite the find.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, what's my next training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Don't get ahead of yourself, Dai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you're the older student,\Nso look after Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Mr. Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I have various training courses,\Nbut we're short on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Dai, you will be taking the\None week hero-making Special Hard Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I can become a Hero in a week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can!\NDon't do it! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can join, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you, Master!\NI'm fine with the normal training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get strong and save Leona\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.\NWe'll begin your hard training tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Not right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Avan is tired from a long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also expended much Magic Power\Ncasting such a powerful spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.\NLet's all get some proper rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could\Nbecome a Hero in just a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BAGIKUROSAI{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NVORTEX-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. The Special Hard Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, slice this with a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! This?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first day's objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I broke the legendary sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!\NI'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NUse your knife instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This sword only cost ten gold coins,\Nso it's only natural.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. I can't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, go run a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll begin\Nthe normal training course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,First is Avan Style Basic Training!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Avan Style Unarmed Combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the basics of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, what sort of training is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's meditation\Nto increase your Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for magic practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The wave froze! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I've been training\Nwith Master for over a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You fail to see things through as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is about focus. Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Dai, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much potential for magic, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to worry\Nabout him overtaking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard training! Sword practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very good.\NHe does show promise in swordplay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NThat man possesses unfathomable skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've never\Nseen Dai train so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it another go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I'm completely beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trust me and give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When people are thoroughly exhausted,\Ntheir movements become simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Ntheir most natural movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You tended to move too much\Nwith your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always had the strength\Nto slice a boulder like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you really are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really sliced it in one day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He really must have been exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, are you really going to continue\Nwith the Special Hard Course?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. His grand objective\Nis to save his friends, so he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you can join us with the morning\Nand evening training if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done. You made me use\Nboth hands in only two days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To improve this much since yesterday\Nis astounding progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As a reward, let me show you\Nmy special move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my super special attack.\NTry to master it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Avan Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Master just went and showed him\Nhis best attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this strong with just a wooden stick?\NThat's an amazing attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you can join\Nthe Special Hard Course anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No thanks!\NI'm fine with the Normal Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:23.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,AVAN STYLE SWORD TECHNIQUE THEORY\NEARTH, SEA, AIR
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The theory\Nof the Avan Style Sword Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth, sea, and air. You will learn\Nto slice these three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth? Sea and air?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's start with\Nthe earth slicing attack, Earth Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to this attack is power.\NIn other words, strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan Style Sword Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Earth Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice.\NYou've almost mastered Earth Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But Earth Slash is the most basic attack.\NI wanna learn Avan Strash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Everything has its proper order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,AVAN STYLE SWORD TECHNIQUE THEORY\NEARTH, SEA, AIR
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slice the earth, slice the sea,\Nslice the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And what slices everything is Avan Strash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're watching, tend to Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Get some rest until dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going\Nto continue this all week?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane. Do you really like\Nthat Papnica Princess that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I do apologize for dinner being so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I get so excited watching Dai's progress\NI get caught up in the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And Popp too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he would never\Ntake his training seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I gave him a hard task,\Nhe'd always give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently, he's been curious about Dai\Nand keeps spying on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, tomorrow's training\Ncould get a little chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a place we can use\Nwhere we won't trouble others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A place that won't cause trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to learn Earth Slash\Nin two days, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, your third day training\Nshall be to learn an even harder skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy.\NIf you aren't careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of training is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Very simple. You will fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I will be using a special spell,\Nso you may use your knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My knife of Papnica?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. My skin will\Nbe harder than steel after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Doragoramu!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Master turned into a Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To learn the Avan Style Sword Technique{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai bravely faces Avan, who changed\Ninto a Dragon using an ancient spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through Avan's training,\NDai rapidly grows stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But an evil presence closes in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Dark Lord Hadlar's Return"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:23:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
